## 64.循环Promise链式调用.md

> 假设有一个数组`const list = [] // 里面全是Promise`，现在需要按顺序依次在上一个执行完后`.then`执行下一个

```js
    const randomNum = (min, max) => {
        return Math.random() * (max - min + 1) + min
    }
    const list = []
    const timeOut = randomNum(1, 1.5) * 1000
    const listLength = Math.floor(randomNum(5, 10))
    console.log(`timeOut为：${timeOut}, listLength为：${listLength}`)
    // 生成随机长度为[5, 10]的Promise数组
    for (let i = 0; i< listLength; i++) {
      list.push(() =>{
        return new Promise(resolve =>{
          setTimeout(() =>{
            console.log('Promise', i + 1, new Date())
            resolve(i + 1)
          }, timeOut)
        })
      })
    }
    const orderPromise = () =>{
      let promise = Promise.resolve()
      return new Promise(resolve =>{
        for (let i = 0; i < list.length; i++) {
          promise = promise.then((res) => list[i]())
          if (i === list.length - 1) {
            resolve(promise)
          }
        }
      })
    }
    orderPromise().then(res =>{
      console.log('结束',res)
    })
```
